<figureCitation box="[159,272,1509,1534]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 12" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1908,1931]" captionTargetBox="[236,1350,210,1878]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[195,1400,193,1894]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 12. Elongationa hyalina sp. nov. 1 habitus, dorsal view; 2, habitus, lateral view; 3, forewing; 4, face; 5, anal tube and appendages, lateral view; 6, pygofer side, lateral view; 7, male 8 th sternite, ventral view; 8, magnified aedeagus, ventral view; 9, aedeagus, style and connective, later view; 10, subgenital plate, ventral view; 11, connective, dorsal view; 12, magnified process of pygofer, ventral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm (Figs. 1 - 7, 9 - 12); 0.4 mm (Figs. 8)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/832730/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="362">Figs 1–12</figureCitation>
)
